nom.bdezonia.zorbage.sampling

Class SamplingCartesianRealGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • nom.bdezonia.zorbage.sampling.SamplingCartesianRealGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Set<RealIndex>, Sampling<RealIndex>, DimensionCount

    public class SamplingCartesianRealGrid
extends java.lang.Object
implements Sampling<RealIndex>
    SamplingCartesianRealGrid is an n-dimensional Sampling that spans a user defined region of Euclidean space. It is defined by two n-dimensional real space points and a set of n counts that determine the spacing along each dimensions.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
